---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
const title = `Not a Square｜実績`;
const description = `Not a Square（NaS AI）の支援実績。建設業におけるAI活用による業務効率化・工数削減の事例（想定モデルケース）をご紹介します。`;
---

<BaseLayout title={title} description={description} active="record">

<section class="page-hero">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="en hero-anim">WORKS</div>
    <h1 class="hero-anim d1">支援実績</h1>
    <div class="breadcrumb hero-anim d2"><a href="/">ホーム</a> ／ 実績</div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ===== CASES ===== -->
<section class="sec sec-light">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="works-filter reveal">
      <button class="wf-tab active" data-filter="all">全ての実績</button>
      <button class="wf-tab" data-filter="防犯設備">防犯設備</button>
    </div>
    <div class="uc-grid">
      <a href="/record-01" class="uc-card uc-link reveal" data-cat="防犯設備">
        <div class="uc-media">
          <span class="uc-tag">防犯設備</span>
          <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1592838064575-70ed626d3a0e?fm=jpg&q=80&w=600&auto=format&fit=crop" alt="">
          <div class="uc-metric">
            <span class="uc-metric-lbl">想定削減工数<span class="uc-metric-est">見込み</span></span>
            <span class="uc-metric-val"><span class="big"><span data-count="35">0</span></span><span class="u">時間/月</span></span>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="uc-body">
          <h3>配車管理の自動連携</h3>
          <p>配車データのカレンダー自動反映によって二重管理や伝達漏れをなくし、事務作業を大幅に効率化しました。</p>
          <div class="uc-meta"><svg width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.7" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M3 7l9-4 9 4-9 4-9-4z"/><path d="M3 7v6l9 4 9-4V7"/></svg>防犯設備業・見込み<span class="uc-more">詳細を見る<svg width="15" height="15" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.9" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M5 12h14M13 6l6 6-6 6"/></svg></span></div>
        </div>
      </a>
      <a href="/record-02" class="uc-card uc-link reveal" data-delay="1" data-cat="防犯設備">
        <div class="uc-media">
          <span class="uc-tag">防犯設備</span>
          <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1554224155-6726b3ff858f?fm=jpg&q=80&w=600&auto=format&fit=crop" alt="">
          <div class="uc-metric">
            <span class="uc-metric-lbl">想定削減工数<span class="uc-metric-est">見込み</span></span>
            <span class="uc-metric-val"><span class="big"><span data-count="50">0</span></span><span class="u">時間/月</span></span>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="uc-body">
          <h3>請求書作成の自動化</h3>
          <p>受注データからの請求書自動生成で転記ミスを防ぎ、月末の締め作業を標準化して属人化を解消しました。</p>
          <div class="uc-meta"><svg width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.7" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M3 7l9-4 9 4-9 4-9-4z"/><path d="M3 7v6l9 4 9-4V7"/></svg>防犯設備業・見込み<span class="uc-more">詳細を見る<svg width="15" height="15" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.9" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M5 12h14M13 6l6 6-6 6"/></svg></span></div>
        </div>
      </a>
      <a href="/record-03" class="uc-card uc-link reveal" data-delay="2" data-cat="防犯設備">
        <div class="uc-media">
          <span class="uc-tag">防犯設備</span>
          <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1551288049-bebda4e38f71?fm=jpg&q=80&w=600&auto=format&fit=crop" alt="">
          <div class="uc-metric">
            <span class="uc-metric-lbl">想定削減工数<span class="uc-metric-est">見込み</span></span>
            <span class="uc-metric-val"><span class="big"><span data-count="45">0</span></span><span class="u">時間/月</span></span>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="uc-body">
          <h3>紙納品書のデータ化</h3>
          <p>現場でスマホ撮影するだけでAIが納品書を自動データ化。現場の負担を増やさず、手入力作業をゼロにしました。</p>
          <div class="uc-meta"><svg width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.7" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M3 7l9-4 9 4-9 4-9-4z"/><path d="M3 7v6l9 4 9-4V7"/></svg>防犯設備業・見込み<span class="uc-more">詳細を見る<svg width="15" height="15" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.9" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M5 12h14M13 6l6 6-6 6"/></svg></span></div>
        </div>
      </a>
    </div>
    <div style="text-align:right;font-size:11px;color:#6B7079;margin-top:18px">※削減時間はすべて見込み（未実測）の数値です。第1号クライアント1社での取り組みであり、御社での効果は現場アセスメント後に確定します。</div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="cta-band">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="reveal-left">
      <div class="ttl">御社でも、同じ成果を。</div>
      <div class="sub">まずは無料相談で、御社の可能性をお聞かせください。</div>
    </div>
    <div class="actions reveal">
      <a href="/download" class="btn btn-pill btn-pill-blue">
        資料をダウンロード
        <svg width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.8" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M12 3v12M7 11l5 4 5-4M5 21h14"/></svg>
      </a>
      <a href="/consultation" class="btn btn-pill btn-pill-warm">
        無料相談を申し込む
        <svg width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.8" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M5 12h14M13 6l6 6-6 6"/></svg>
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style is:inline>
  /* ===== record page (modern) ===== */
  .works-filter{display:flex;gap:12px;flex-wrap:wrap;justify-content:center;margin-bottom:36px}
  .wf-tab{font-family:inherit;font-size:13.5px;font-weight:700;color:#3A3F47;background:#fff;border:1px solid #d8dfea;border-radius:30px;padding:11px 30px;cursor:pointer;transition:background .25s,border-color .25s,color .25s,box-shadow .25s}
  .wf-tab:hover{border-color:#14233F;color:#14233F}
  .wf-tab.active{background:#14233F;border-color:#14233F;color:#fff;box-shadow:0 8px 20px rgba(28,59,117,.2)}
  .uc-grid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(3,1fr);gap:24px}
  .uc-meta{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:7px;margin-top:auto;padding-top:14px;border-top:1px solid #eef1f6;font-size:12px;color:#6B7079}
  .uc-more{margin-left:auto;display:inline-flex;align-items:center;gap:5px;font-weight:700;color:#14233F}
  .uc-link{text-decoration:none;color:inherit;cursor:pointer}
  .uc-card{background:#fff;border-radius:18px;overflow:hidden;border:1px solid #e7ebf3;display:flex;flex-direction:column;transition:transform .35s cubic-bezier(.2,.7,.2,1),box-shadow .35s}
  .uc-card:hover{transform:translateY(-7px);box-shadow:0 26px 50px rgba(16,32,63,.16)}
  .uc-media{position:relative;height:172px;overflow:hidden}
  .uc-media img{width:100%;height:100%;object-fit:cover;transition:transform .6s cubic-bezier(.2,.7,.2,1);filter:brightness(102%) saturate(108%)}
  .uc-card:hover .uc-media img{transform:scale(1.07)}
  .uc-media::after{content:"";position:absolute;inset:0;background:linear-gradient(180deg,rgba(16,32,63,0) 40%,rgba(16,32,63,.55) 100%)}
  .uc-tag{position:absolute;top:14px;left:14px;z-index:2;background:rgba(255,255,255,.92);color:#14233F;font-size:11px;font-weight:700;padding:5px 12px;border-radius:30px;letter-spacing:.04em}
  .uc-metric{position:absolute;left:16px;bottom:14px;z-index:2;color:#fff;display:inline-flex;flex-direction:column;align-items:flex-start;gap:2px;background:rgba(16,32,63,.4);backdrop-filter:blur(6px);-webkit-backdrop-filter:blur(6px);border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.16);border-radius:12px;padding:9px 14px}
  .uc-metric-lbl{display:inline-flex;align-items:center;gap:6px;font-size:10.5px;font-weight:700;letter-spacing:.03em;color:#cfdef3}
  .uc-metric-est{font-size:9px;font-weight:700;color:#14233F;background:rgba(255,255,255,.9);padding:2px 6px;border-radius:20px;letter-spacing:.02em}
  .uc-metric-val{display:flex;align-items:baseline;gap:3px}
  .uc-metric .big{font-family:'Fraunces','Times New Roman',serif;font-optical-sizing:auto;font-size:32px;font-weight:600;line-height:1}
  .uc-metric .u{font-size:11.5px;font-weight:700;color:#dfeaf8}
  .uc-body{padding:22px 24px 26px;flex:1;display:flex;flex-direction:column}
  .uc-body h3{font-size:16.5px;font-weight:700;margin:0 0 10px}
  .uc-body p{font-size:12.8px;color:#3A3F47;line-height:1.9;margin:0}

  @media(max-width:860px){
    .uc-grid{grid-template-columns:1fr}
  }
</style>
<script is:inline>
  (function(){
    var tabs = document.querySelectorAll('.wf-tab');
    var cards = document.querySelectorAll('.uc-card[data-cat]');
    tabs.forEach(function(tab){
      tab.addEventListener('click', function(){
        tabs.forEach(function(t){ t.classList.remove('active'); });
        tab.classList.add('active');
        var f = tab.getAttribute('data-filter');
        cards.forEach(function(c){
          c.style.display = (f === 'all' || c.getAttribute('data-cat') === f) ? '' : 'none';
        });
      });
    });
  })();
</script>
</BaseLayout>
